.Sh NAME
.Nm vidcontrol
.Nd "a utility for manipulating the syscons console driver"
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl b Ar color
.Op Fl c Ar appearance
.Op Fl d
.Oo
.Fl f
.Op Ar size
.Ar file
.Oc
.Op Fl g Ar geometry
.Op Fl i Cm adapter | mode
.Op Fl l Ar screen_map
.Op Fl L
.Op Fl M Ar char
.Op Fl m Cm on | off
.Op Fl p
